Computes the connex components of a graph, represented by an adjacency matrix.

Source: R/ConnectedComps.R, R/mod_ds_cc.R
connected-components.Rd

This function computes the connex components of a graph, represented by an adjacency matrix.

Method to build the list of connected components of an adjacency matrix

Builds a graph as defined by its nodes and edges.

Displays a connected component as a graph with the package 'visNetwork'.

Jitter plot of CC

Display a jitter plot for connex component with the package highcharter

A shiny Module.

A vector of strings which are the text for the tooltips of the peptides.
